-- Societe Generale in Exclusive Talks With Econocom With View to Sale of ECS
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-01T05:39:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/societe-generale-in-exclusive-talks-with-econocom-with-view-to-sale-of-ecs.html

          
          
             Societe Generale SA said that it’s in
exclusive talks with Econocom Group SA with a view to selling
its ECS information-systems management unit.  
 Econocom’s bid values ECS at 210 million euros, Societe
Generale said in an emailed statement. Societe Generale would
take a 9 percent stake in Econocom as part of the accord.  
          
          


  


        